Class DefineBitsJPEG2

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class DefineBitsJPEG2
extends DefinitionTag

Defines a bitmap character with JPEG compression. It contains both the JPEG encoding table and the JPEG image data, allowing multiple JPEG images with differing encoding tables to be defined within a SWF file

Since:
SWF 2
